description: Welcome to this spacious new build house with garden space. The property is situated close to main amenities such as the high street which has major supermarkets and some local restaurants all within a 3 min drive or 15 min walk from the property. A private room & private bathroom (not en-suite) within the property is available for a working professional, solo traveller or for a couples get away. Free parking for one vehicle is also available at the property
